1490, from {{etyl|frm}} {{term|mignon||lover, royal favourite, darling}}, from {{etyl|fro}} {{term|mignot||dainty, pleasing, gentle, kind|lang=fro}}, from {{etyl|frk}} {{recons|minnjo||love, friendship, affection, memory|lang=frk}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{recons|minþiō|lang=gem-pro}}, {{recons|mindiō||affectionate thought, care|lang=gem-pro}}, from {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} {{recons|men-|lang=ine-pro}}, {{recons|mnā-||to think|lang=ine-pro}}. Cognate with {{etyl|goh|-}} {{term|minnja||love, care, affection, desire, memory|lang=goh}}, {{etyl|osx|-}} {{term|minnea||love|lang=osx}}. More at {{l|en|mind}}.

